DTSTAMP:20260312T024459Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260315T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260315T223000
SUMMARY:Baila in the West Sunday Social
DESCRIPTION:Salsa | Bachata | Kizomba GTA\nBest way to get a hold of us is
  on our [WhatsApp chat](https://chat.whatsapp.com/Kj63TzHIqYL5hPrRJolhyD)\
 , also great way to join a community of amazing like-minded people :)\n\n*
 **Let's Dance!***\n***¡Vamos a bailar!***\n\n***DJ Geronimo 🎧 will be 
 playing your favorite Salsa 🎵 Bachata 🎶 Chacha 🎵 Merengue hits 
 🔊 DJ Sweetlike will be jamming in the Kizomba room***\n\nCover $10 befo
 re 7pm - $15 after 7pm - includes:\n***Free Bachata and Kizomba Lesson at 
 6pm (you choose)***\n***Dancing til 10:30pm***\n\n***\\*Casual dress code*
 **\n***\\*Bring your own refreshments***\n\n***👠Please wear comfortable
  & clean shoes👞***\n\n**Location:**\n161 Lakeshore Rd W\, @ Mississauga
  Rd
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/salsa-bachata-kizomba-gta/events/3134
 99360/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260223T234901Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260223T234901Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
